{"tid":2322383,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【姿色改變命運】因疫情丟百萬年薪工作   美女教師改賣性感辣照月入90萬","createTime":"2020-12-12T09:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T10:04:14.000Z","uid":293677,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ca64793c239f0eaafa1085a4277d73c4180ad7","tid":2322383,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/12/12/php6JkdRH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F12%2F12%2Fphp6JkdRH.jpg&h=d2438ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖擷自IG@rileysummers.tv）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020/12/12 16:17<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情害得全球許多人失業，美國一名23歲女老師萊莉（Riley Summers）也是苦主，因為學校停課害自己被裁員，失去年薪百萬的教職工作，為了生存她改行當起網紅，在社群媒體上分享自己的性感自拍照，沒想到卻意外爆紅，現在每週收入都高達英鎊6000元（約新台幣22.3萬元）。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，因為武漢肺炎疫情緣故，萊莉原本任教的學校停課，害她丟了年薪英鎊2萬7000元（約新台幣100萬元）的教職工作，但生活總得繼續，生計總得維持，原本生性害羞的萊莉，便開始在Insatgram上當起模特兒。<br />\n<br />\n身材姣好、長相甜美的萊莉馬上就在在Instagram上深受網友喜愛，她更是在成人收費影音平台開設頻道，靠著上傳自己的性感照片及影片，不但有超過120萬名粉絲追蹤，每週收入更高達英鎊6000元，遠勝以前教職的收入。<br />\n<br />\n萊莉說，雖然她丟了工作，「但上帝幫我開了另一扇窗」，她說自己原本對社群媒體非常陌生，但做了之後便深深愛上了它，並讓她因分享自己的性感照而得到喜悅與自信，「每次只要分享一張淘氣的照片，我的腎上腺素都會激增」。<br />\n<br />\n萊莉也說，和粉絲互動時，會覺得自己好像與眾不同，「儘管我和他們的生活可能都很普通，不過他們喜歡我是因為我的外表，我覺得這樣很好」。此外，萊莉也表示，目前有交往對象，不過每天都在被「潛在求婚者」的讚美淹沒，讓她覺得很高興。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3379442\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3379442&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jchPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=bfe3dd04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3379442&h=8b9702e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3379442</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"limegreen\"><strong>呢個故事，真係好勵志喔！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"2485e5a6ab54df58f59bd6cdf9406d8caed9900c","tid":2322383,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f715bb6a851d40f96da5f66fe6aa411028571e5","tid":2322383,"uid":110332,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"我都想有閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6351e090887f4e409a92088f70c065c2b50f1f2","tid":2322383,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b7fb0d8f2680e93db7ca4a2e40eaf27a7321aed","tid":2322383,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f6351e090887f4e409a92088f70c065c2b50f1f2","tid":2322383,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2485e5a6ab54df58f59bd6cdf9406d8caed9900c","tid":2322383,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"有眼？"},{"pid":"a8ac1fed57b50e947303a398f2c98af30af847db","tid":2322383,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:45:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80fd58e6b0cb45a11dff8f0ff2f273f13347267b","tid":2322383,"uid":199237,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b26e98d3a3c5974d5f70aa42a7e549bf906f86f2","tid":2322383,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:47:13.000Z","msg":"黃子華：呢件事非常勵志，證明一個人就算識好少嘢，都搵到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e345892437c6ecca4c2a56a44c71636c04adae6","tid":2322383,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"80fd58e6b0cb45a11dff8f0ff2f273f13347267b","tid":2322383,"uid":199237,"lik